âœ… Topic 2: Amazon Lightsail
ğŸ”¹ What is it?
Amazon Lightsail is a simplified cloud platform designed for developers, small businesses, or beginners to launch and manage virtual private servers (VPS) easily.

âš™ï¸ Use Case:
